The Model View Controller - MVC


*Separation of Concerns

Model
-representing data in your code
-work with data => save , fetch
--- usually used for database schema and methods, structure of data => ex. a product

Views
- what user sees
- rendering the right content
- decoupled from your application code


Controllers
- connecting your models and your views
- contains in-between logic
===> may be split across middleware functions

*Routes
